extends layout
block content
  .hero
    .hero-inner
      .hero-copy.hero-portfolio
        h1 Portfolio
        p
          | A small sample of my web development work and experiments.
        p
          | Don't forget to check my
          a(href="http://codepen.io/crisberrios/")= ' Codepen '
          | and
          a(href="http://www.github.com/crisberrios")= ' Githhub '
          | profiles for more projects and samples.
  section.main
    .cards
      .card
        .card-image
          img(src='/img/kopernik.png', alt='Kopernik')
        .card-header
          | Kopernik's Wonder Women Initiative
        .card-copy
          p
            | Data capture solution with offline capabilities for use in remote regions of Indonesia. You can see more information in
            a(href="http://blog.freecodecamp.com/2015/04/kopernik-retrospective-my-first-nonprofit-project-at-free-code-camp.html")= ' This Post'
      .card
        .card-image
          img(src='/img/webdevnews.jpg', alt='WebDevNews')
        .card-header
          | WebDevNews
        .card-copy
          p
            | A Reddit-like, real-time social news site using React components and Firebase backend with authentication. In progress. Visit the
            a(href="https://blazing-fire-230.firebaseapp.com/")= ' Demo'
            | .
      .card
        .card-image
          img(src='/img/react-starter.jpg', alt='React Starter')
        .card-header
          | React Starter
        .card-copy
          p
            | Frontend project boilerplate using React and integrated workflow.This project is based on gulp-starter and also includes Babel, Jade, HTML5 Boilerplate, Normalize.css, html5shiv, Bourbon, Neat and Bitters in a Browserify/Gulp workflow. Visit the
            a(href="https://github.com/crisberrios/react-starter")= ' Repository'
